ted: I said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, instruct me.\u201d The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cI advise you to fear Allah Almighty, for it will beautify all of your affairs.\u201d I said, \u201cTell me more.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cYou must recite the Quran and remember\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32272,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/18\/abu-dharr-loves-allah-rasul\/","url_meta":{"origin":26198,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Faith: Abu Dharr loves Allah and His Messenger","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 18, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Dharr reported: He said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, a man loves a people, but he cannot do good deeds like they do.\u201d The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cYou, O Abu Dharr, will be with those you love.\u201d Abu Dharr said, \u201cI love Allah\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":35660,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/04\/15\/ayn-insane-suicidal\/","url_meta":{"origin":26198,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on \u2018Ayn: Evil eye can drive a man insane, suicidal","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 15, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Dharr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, the evil eye might attach itself to a man by permission of Allah, until he climbs a tall mountain and then throws himself off it.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 21471 Grade: Hasan li ghayrihi (fair due\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15451,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/28\/salaam-permission-enter-home\/","url_meta":{"origin":26198,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Salaam: Greet with peace when asking permission","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 28, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Rib\u2019i ibn Hirash reported: A man from the tribe of 'Amir sought permission to enter the home of the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him. The man said, \u201cMay I enter?\u201d The Prophet said to his servant, \u201cGo out to this man and teach him how to ask permission\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":5596,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/27\/tawbah-by-night-and-day\/","url_meta":{"origin":26198,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Tawbah: Allah accepts repentance night and day","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 27, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Musa reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, Allah Almighty stretches out His hand by night to accept the repentance of those who sin by day, and He stretches out His hand by day to accept the repentance of those who sin by night, until\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u0